elements.name: As a user I edit the timezone of the site

steps.name: I set scenario "Manage_settings_change_timezone" and version app "<VERSION>"
I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having xpath "(//a[@class='ember-view'])[8]"
I click on element having xpath "(//button[@class='gh-btn'])[2]"
I select option with value "Pacific/Honolulu" for dropdown having xpath "//select[@class='ember-view']"
I click on element having xpath "//button[@class='gh-btn gh-btn-blue gh-btn-icon ember-view']"
I verify "Pacific/Honolulu" into input field having xpath "//select[@class='ember-view']"
